T1  - CEO Contracting and Antitakeover Amendments
AU  - BOROKHOVICH, KENNETH A.
AU  - BRUNARSKI, KELLY R.
AU  - PARRINO, ROBERT
Y1  - 1997/09/01
PY  - 1997
DA  - 1997/09/01
